sources.title: When the Girls Take Over (1962) PSYCHOTRONIC
sources.description:
It's Friday@PizzaFLIX
Producer/Director: Russell Hayden
Stars: Robert Lowery, Marvin Miller, Jackie Coogan, and James Ellison

When the little Caribbean island of Hondo-Rica is threatened by a revolutionist, an American Oil Tycoon raises a task force of twenty-six pink jeeps filled with wine, women, and food to save the republic! Watch for Gabriel Dell of The Dead End Kids/East Side Kids/Bowery Boys fame.

Trivia: #3,039 in Michael J. Weldon's Psychotronic Encyclopedia of Film, an 815-page compilation of mini-reviews of over 3,000 cult films.

metadata.Plot: A comic look - at Cuba after the Castro regime take-over.
metadata.Actors: Robert Lowery, Marvin Miller, Jackie Coogan
